{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "7b1f2a91-4f17-4d6a-a5d4-nodejs-skillup-users",
    "name": "Week2 Express Users",
    "description": "Week2 Express users API 的手动测试集,按 demo 推荐顺序排列。\n\n- 「一、黄金路径」按顺序从上到下点,靠 Test 脚本自动把上一步的 _id/邮箱存进 collection variable,不用手动复制粘贴。\n- 「二/三/四、边界与错误场景」按状态码分组(400 → 404 → 409),三个文件夹互相不依赖；400/404 文件夹内部每条也互相独立，挑着点没问题；409 文件夹内部有顺序依赖(seed → 测试 → 清理)，要按顺序整组跑，见该文件夹自己的说明。\n- 对应的 VS Code REST Client 版本见 users.http,分组和顺序保持一致。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "一、黄金路径 · 完整生命周期演示",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. List users - 创建前的基线",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 200。演示前先看一眼现有列表,方便对比创建后的变化。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Create user - 成功创建",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Demo User\",\n  \"email\": \"demo-user-{{$timestamp}}@example.com\",\n  \"age\": 28,\n  \"addresses\": [\n    {\n      \"recipient\": \"Demo User\",\n      \"phone\": \"13800000000\",\n      \"province\": \"Shanghai\",\n      \"city\": \"Shanghai\",\n      \"detailAddress\": \"Demo Road 1\"\n    }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 201 + 新用户对象(带 MongoDB 生成的 _id)。Test 脚本会自动把 _id 存进 demoUserId,后续请求直接复用,不用手动复制。"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('status is 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('demoUserId', data._id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "3. List users - 创建后,确认新用户出现在列表里",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 200,数组里能找到上一步创建的 demoUserId。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Get user by id - 读取刚创建的用户",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoUserId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{demoUserId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 200,内容和 Create 返回的一致。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Update user - 局部更新(只改 name/age)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoUserId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{demoUserId}}"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Demo User (Updated)\",\n  \"age\": 35\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 200,返回更新后的对象;email/addresses 应保持不变(局部更新语义)。"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status is 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('name updated', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().name).to.eql('Demo User (Updated)'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Get user by id - 确认更新已持久化",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoUserId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{demoUserId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 200,name/age 是更新后的新值。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "7. Delete user - 删除",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoUserId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{demoUserId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 200 + 提示 message。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "8. Get user by id - 确认已删除",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{demoUserId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{demoUserId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 404,证明删除真实生效,不是接口\"假装成功\"。"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "二、边界与错误场景 · 400(格式/校验)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get user - invalid ObjectId format",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/1",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "1"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 400,id 不是合法的 24 位十六进制 ObjectId。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create user - missing email",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Missing Email User\",\n  \"age\": 20\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 400,email 是 Model 里的必填字段。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create user - missing name",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"missing-name-{{$timestamp}}@example.com\",\n  \"age\": 20\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 400,name 是 Model 里的必填字段。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create user - invalid email format",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Bad Email User\",\n  \"email\": \"not-an-email\",\n  \"age\": 20\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 400,Model 的 `match` 校验拒绝非法邮箱格式。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update user - invalid ObjectId format",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/1",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "1"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Updated User Name\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 400,id 不是合法的 24 位十六进制 ObjectId。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update user - empty body (no valid fields)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{missingUserId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{missingUserId}}"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 400 \"No valid fields provided to update\"——body 里挑不出任何可更新字段,在碰数据库前就被挡下。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete user - invalid ObjectId format",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/1",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "1"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 400,id 不是合法的 24 位十六进制 ObjectId。"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "三、边界与错误场景 · 404(不存在)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get user - valid format, no matching user",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{missingUserId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{missingUserId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 404,格式合法但没有任何用户拥有这个 _id。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update user - valid format, no matching user",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{missingUserId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{missingUserId}}"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ghost User\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 404。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete user - valid format, no matching user",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{missingUserId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{missingUserId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expected: 404。"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "四、边界与错误场景 · 409(邮箱冲突)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create seed user A (占用一个邮箱)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Seed User A\",\n  \"email\": \"seed-a-{{$timestamp}}@example.com\",\n  \"age\": 30\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 201。Test 脚本自动把邮箱和 _id 存进 seedUserAEmail / seedUserAId,给下面几条 409/清理用。"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('seedUserAEmail', data.email);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('seedUserAId', data._id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Create seed user B (用来测试改成别人的邮箱)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Seed User B\",\n  \"email\": \"seed-b-{{$timestamp}}@example.com\",\n  \"age\": 31\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 201。Test 脚本自动把 _id 存进 seedUserBId。"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('seedUserBId', data._id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Create user - duplicate email",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Duplicate Email Attempt\",\n  \"email\": \"{{seedUserAEmail}}\",\n  \"age\": 32\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 409,邮箱和 Seed User A 撞了。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update user - duplicate email",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{seedUserBId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{seedUserBId}}"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{seedUserAEmail}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Expected: 409,把 Seed User B 的邮箱改成 Seed User A 的,验证错误翻译链在 update 路径同样生效。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "清理:删除 Seed User A",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{seedUserAId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{seedUserAId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "不留 demo 垃圾数据。Expected: 200。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "清理:删除 Seed User B",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{seedUserBId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "{{seedUserBId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "不留 demo 垃圾数据。Expected: 200。"
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "这个文件夹内部有顺序依赖，前 4 条按顺序执行：先跑两条 Create seed（A/B），再跑两条 409 测试（依赖 seed 的邮箱/_id）；最后两条 清理 用来删掉 seed 用户，不留垃圾数据。跟其他边界文件夹（400/404）不同，这里不能挑着单独点。"
    }
  ],
